      <p>Ownership is straightforward. Replacement parts are accessible, support is generally easier than with niche imports, and the workflow stays manageable even for first-time burr grinder buyers. If you want a low-regret purchase with room to grow your skills, this is the safest recommendation in this bracket.</p>
